      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/3/52/1",
      "text": [
        " قَالَ عَلِيٌّ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ : \"أَوْلاَدُ اَلْمُشْرِكِينَ مَعَ آبَائِهِمْ فِي اَلنَّارِ وَ أَوْلاَدُ اَلْمُسْلِمِينَ مَعَ آبَائِهِمْ فِي اَلْجَنَّةِ \"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.4739 - Wahb ibn Wahb narrated from Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) from his father, Imam Muhammad ibn Ali Al-Baqir (as), who said that Imam Ali ibn Abi Talib (as) said:\n\"The children of polytheists will be with their parents in the Fire, and the children of Muslims will be with their parents in Paradise.\""
        ]
      }
    },
